# maisonDeux Project Overview

- Monorepo workspaces:
  - `apps/api` (Fastify API + worker + adapters + Prisma)
  - `apps/mobile` (Expo React Native app)
  - `packages/shared` (canonical types and trust/query helpers)
- Search flow:
  1. API validates request and creates `Search`
  2. Queue enqueues `search-jobs` (or inline fallback)
  3. Worker runs `processSearch()` fan-out
  4. Results normalize to `CanonicalListing`, persist, rank, return via polling
- Key backend files:
  - `apps/api/src/server.ts`
  - `apps/api/src/services/search-pipeline.ts`
  - `apps/api/src/adapters.ts`
  - `apps/api/prisma/schema.prisma`
- Key mobile files:
  - `apps/mobile/src/store.ts` (`useMaisonDeuxStore`)
  - `apps/mobile/src/api.ts`
  - `apps/mobile/src/screens/*`
- Public domains currently expected to stay healthy:
  - `maisondeux.vip`
  - `www.maisondeux.vip`
  - `ig.subwayarcade.org`
